Modules:  dotenv,express,mongoose,cors 

>npm init -y 
>npm i morgan
>npm i chalk
>npm i dotenv express mongoose cors

DB Schema 


Database LOCAL URL: mongodb://localhost:27017/papi

Table/collection: product 

Feilds:   name:String , 
          price:number, 
          image:String,
          qty:number,
          info:String,
          created:date 


How to read configuration env values?
dontenv module 


What is model?
model:product 
